This topic explains how to install <%= vars.platform_name %> on GCP manually.

## <a id="overview"></a> Overview

You can install <%= vars.platform_name %> on GCP with either the <%= vars.app_runtime_full %> (<%= vars.app_runtime_abbr %>) or <%= vars.k8s_runtime_full %> (<%= vars.k8s_runtime_abbr %>) runtime.

To install <%= vars.platform_name %> on GCP manually, do one of the following:

* Install with <%= vars.app_runtime_abbr %>. See [Install with <%= vars.app_runtime_abbr %>](#manual-pas).
* Install with <%= vars.k8s_runtime_abbr %>. See [Install with <%= vars.k8s_runtime_abbr %>](#manual-pks).

## <a id="manual-pas"></a> Install with <%= vars.app_runtime_abbr %>

To install manually with <%= vars.app_runtime_abbr %>, do the following:

1. Prepare to deploy Ops Manager. See [Preparing to Deploy Ops Manager on GCP](/platform/ops-manager/<%= vars.current_major_version.sub('.','-') %>/gcp/prepare-env-manual.html).

1. Deploy Ops Manager. See [Deploying Ops Manager on GCP](/platform/ops-manager/<%= vars.current_major_version.sub('.','-') %>/gcp/deploy-manual.html).

1. Configure BOSH Director. See [Configuring BOSH Director on GCP](/platform/ops-manager/<%= vars.current_major_version.sub('.','-') %>/gcp/config-manual.html).

1. (Optional). Configure a shared VPC. See [(Optional) Configuring a Shared VPC on GCP](./gcp-shared-vpc.html).

## <a id="manual-pks"></a> Install with <%= vars.k8s_runtime_abbr %>

To install manually with <%= vars.k8s_runtime_abbr %>, do the following:

1. Prepare to deploy Ops Manager. See [Preparing to Deploy Ops Manager on GCP](/platform/ops-manager/<%= vars.current_major_version.sub('.','-') %>/gcp/prepare-env-manual.html).

1. Deploy Ops Manager. See [Deploying Ops Manager on GCP](/platform/ops-manager/<%= vars.current_major_version.sub('.','-') %>/gcp/deploy-manual.html).

1. Configure BOSH Director. See [Configuring BOSH Director on GCP](/platform/ops-manager/<%= vars.current_major_version.sub('.','-') %>/gcp/config-manual.html).

1. (Optional). Configure a shared VPC. See [(Optional) Configuring a Shared VPC on GCP](./gcp-shared-vpc.html).

